The #AmINext movement has brought to the surface feelings of anger, fear and frustration. News24 wants to hear what South Africans think. If you could speak to the nation right now, what would you say? Making a submission is simple: 1) Either write a letter of no more than 700 words or send a video of no longer than three minutes. 2) Provide us with your name, age and the province you live in. 3) Email your submissions to saysomething@24.com, with the subject line Dear South Africa #AmINext? 4) Submissions close at 23:59 on September 13. Please note: News24 reserves the right to edit submissions for grammar, accuracy and legal/ethical issues. We're looking forward to hearing what you have to say!